                "post_excerpt": "<div><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[metaslider_hide devices=\"desktop,laptop,tablet\"]<\/span> <h2 style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(236, 240, 241); line-height: 1em;\">Your Environment Shapes Your Focus<\/h2> <p data-start=\"1041\" data-end=\"1247\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[\/metaslider_hide]<\/span><\/p> <p data-start=\"1041\" data-end=\"1247\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[metaslider_hide devices=\"smartphone\"]<\/span><\/p> <h3 data-start=\"992\" data-end=\"1039\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(236, 240, 241);\">Your Environment Shapes Your Focus<\/span><\/h3> <p style=\"line-height: 1;\" data-start=\"1041\" data-end=\"1247\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Where you work matters more than most people realize. A dedicated workspace&mdash;even a small one&mdash;signals your brain that it&rsquo;s time to focus. It doesn&rsquo;t need to be fancy, but it should be consistent.<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[\/metaslider_hide]<\/span><\/p> <\/div>",
