                "post_excerpt": "<div>[metaslider_hide devices=\"desktop,laptop,tablet\"] <h2 style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(236, 240, 241); line-height: 1em;\">Rest Is Part of Productivity<\/h2> <p data-start=\"1959\" data-end=\"2000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[\/metaslider_hide]<\/span><\/p> <p data-start=\"1959\" data-end=\"2000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[metaslider_hide devices=\"smartphone\"]<\/span><\/p> <h3 data-start=\"1959\" data-end=\"2000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; color: rgb(236, 240, 241);\">Rest Is Part of Productivity<\/span><\/h3> <p style=\"line-height: 1;\" data-start=\"1959\" data-end=\"2000\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Working nonstop may feel productive, but it often leads to burnout and diminishing returns. Regular breaks help reset your focus and maintain energy throughout the day.<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">[\/metaslider_hide]<\/span><\/p> <\/div>",
